1. Ona se oseća *sigurno* u svom novom domu. (She feels safe in her new home.)
2. On je *siguran* da će uspeti na ispitu. (He is sure he will pass the exam.)
3. Oni su *sigurni* da će dobiti nagradu. (They are sure they will get the award.)
4. Ona je *sigurna* da će dobiti nagradu. (She is sure she will get the award.)
5. Oni veruju da će biti *sigurni* u tome. (They believe they will be safe in that.)